snippet.title: Jelly no Puzzle for Android
snippet.description: The success from the PC world is now available for Androids. Jelly no Puzzle is a real challenging puzzle game. You move coloured friendly-faced gel blocks left or right. The goal is to bring all blocks of the same colour together. Although it looks simple when you see it, the challenge is really tough!!! The game demands you take your brain an extra step forward.
